quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  68,16,"Men waЙ—anay mo maande nde momtotaako ka hoore kinal makko."
  68,17,"Men jarribor Й“ee sirkooЙ“e kokke e heege, wano Men jarribornoo jeyЙ“e ngesa ba, fewndo Й“en woondunoo wonnde pellet, Й“e soГұiroyay mba subaka on, hiЙ“e hittina fii wata miskiino Гұaamu e mabba."
  68,18,"ЖҒe ronki ittintinnde e woondoore maЙ“Й“e nden, wi'ugol : "Si Allah jaЙ“ii"."
  68,19,"Allah wuurti yiite e mabba, nge Гұaami ba tawi Й“e e mabba hari hiЙ“e Й—aani, Й“e waawaali duГұugol yiite e mabba."
  68,20,"Mba Й“awliri wa jemma niЙ“Й“o."
  68,21,"ЖҒe noddindiri bimmbi law."
  68,22,"ЖҒe wi'i : Dawee ka ngesa mon ado waasuЙ“e Й“en arude, si tawii ko on soГұooЙ“e mba."
  68,23,"ЖҒe yahiri ka ngesa maЙ“Й“e hiЙ“e sowndondira hakkunde maЙ“Й“e."
  68,24,"HiЙ“e wi'indira hakkunde maЙ“Й“e : miskiino woo naatataa ka ngesa ton hannde."
  68,25,"ЖҒe dawidi e eЙ“Й“oore Й—awugol dimЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en."
  68,26,"Nde Й“e yi'noo ngesa mban no huЙ“Й“a, Й“e wi'i: Pellet, men majjii laawol amen ngol."
  68,27,"Wurin ko men haЙ—aaЙ“e suГұugol dimЙ—e amen Й—en, sabu ko men eЙ“Й“unoo kon Й—awugol miskimЙ“e Й“en."
  68,28,"ЖҒurЙ—o moЖҙЖҙude on wi'i: Mi wi'anaano on fewndo eЙ“Й“unoЙ—on Й—awugol waasuЙ“e Й“en : haanii ka subhinanoЙ—on Allah, tuubanon Mo?"
  68,29,"ЖҒe wi'i : Senayee woodanii Joomi amen ! Pellet, hari men tooГұitorii pittaali amen eЙ“Й“ugol Й—awude waasuЙ“e Й“en Й—ee dimЙ—e amen."
  68,30,"ЖҒe ruttitii e konngol maЙ“Й“e ngol, hiЙ“e felitoo."
  68,31,"ЖҒe ninnsi Й“e wi'i : Ee bone amen ! Pellet, hari ko men yawtunooЙ“e keeri, sabu ko men Й—awi kon waasuЙ“e Й“en haqqee maЙ“Й“e."
  68,32,"Hino gasa ka Joomi amen wattitana men ngesa mban. Ko ka Joomi amen tun woni ko menen men rerЙ—anta. Men jortorii Mo yaafuyee, meЙ—en Й—aЙ“Й“ira Mo moЖҙЖҙere."
  68,33,"Ko sugu Й—ee lette haЙ—eede arsike Й—oo, woni ko Men lettirta yeddayЙ“e Men Й“en; ko lette laakara Й—en non Й“uri mawnude, sinno hiЙ“e anndunoo tiiЙ—ugol e duumagol Й—e ngol."
  68,34,"HuluЙ“e Allah Й“en Й—oftii yamirooje Makko Й—en Й“e woЙ—Й—titii haЙ—aaЙ—i Makko Й—in, ko pellet, hino woodani Й“e ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e, Aljannaaji neema, Й—i Й“e neeminotoo e mun, ko aldaa e taЖҙondiral."
  68,35,"Kere Men waЙ—ay juulЙ“e Й“en wano heeferЙ“e Й“en ka njoЙ“di, wano sirkooЙ“e Makka Й“en aaЖҙori Й—um?"
  68,36,"Ko heЙ“i on onon Й“ee sirkooЙ“e, si tawii hiЙ—on Гұaawira ndee Гұaawoore ooГұiinde?"
  68,37,"Kaa hiЙ—on mari Deftere, nde janngoton e mun wiide Й—oftiiЙ—o e goopЙ—o no fota?"
  68,38,"Pellet, ko woodani on e nde Deftere, ko ko suЙ“oytoЙ—on ka laakara."
  68,39,"Kaa ko aadiiji teentinaaЙ—i woodani on e Amen, wonnde pellet, ko ko ГұaawanЙ—on ko'e-mon kon woodani on?"
  68,40,"An NulaaЙ—o, lamndii Й“e wowlu Й“e ngol konngol Й“en, ko hommbo e maЙ“Й“e fawtanii Й“e Й—um?"
  68,41,"Kaa ko kafidaaЙ—i woodani Й“e gaanin Allah, fotnayЙ—i Й“e e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en njoЙ“di? Awa yo Й“e addu Й—in kafidaaЙ—i maЙ“Й“e, si tawii ko e goonga Й“e woni nodditorde fotnugol Й“e e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en ka njoЙ“di."
  68,42,"Г‘alnde Darngal, kulol ngol feeГұay, Joomi men feГұГұina korlal Makko ngal, yimЙ“e Й“en noddee e sujjugol : gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en sujja, heddoo heeferЙ“e Й“en e naafiqiiЙ“e Й“en tawde Й“e waawoytaa sujjude."